cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.SI, cs.CY 

This paper involves machine learning techniques to cluster player behavior and predict win/loss outcomes in online multiplayer games. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.GT (Game Theory). Additionally, the paper involves analyzing player behavior and team composition, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
